      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is QuillBot?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">QuillBot is an AI paraphrasing and writing assistant that rewrites existing text across seven modes, checks grammar, summarizes documents, generates citations, translates content, and checks plagiarism. It serves 50+ million users globally and was acquired by Course Hero (now Learneo) in 2022.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much does QuillBot cost?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Free: $0 with 125-word paraphrasing limit. Premium: $20/month, $13.33/month semi-annually, or $10/month billed annually. The annual plan is the best value if you use it regularly.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is QuillBot free?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes, with limitations. The free tier offers paraphrasing (125-word maximum per input), basic grammar checking, and a 1,200-word summarizer. Premium removes these limits and adds all 7 modes plus plagiarism detection.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does QuillBot help with SEO?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">No. QuillBot has zero SEO features — no keyword research, no competitor analysis, no content optimization, no publishing. Paraphrased content doesn't rank on Google either. For SEO content, theStacc is the alternative.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is using QuillBot for content spinning safe for SEO?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">No. Google's Helpful Content Update specifically targets low-quality derivative material produced through paraphrasing. Rewritten articles receive ranking suppression regardless of which tool you use to rewrite them.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How does QuillBot compare to Grammarly?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">QuillBot surpasses Grammarly in paraphrasing — Grammarly doesn't offer this feature at all. Grammarly outperforms in grammar precision, tone detection, and AI writing quality. QuillBot costs less ($10 vs $12 annually). Neither has SEO features.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
