        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What are the best QuillBot alternatives?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Grammarly ($12/month annual) for grammar; Wordtune ($25/month) for comparable paraphrasing; theStacc ($49/month) for done-for-you SEO content with auto-publishing. The right tool depends entirely on your job.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does QuillBot work with WordPress?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
